Full-control tool suite  (src/advanced/)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The 150+ "full control" tools — the vendored `GodotServer` (src/advanced/
godot-server.ts), the shared utilities (src/advanced/utils.ts), and the two
Godot-side engines (src/advanced/scripts/godot_operations.gd and
src/advanced/scripts/mcp_interaction_server.gd) — are vendored from:

  godot-mcp by Tugcan Topaloglu
  https://github.com/tugcantopaloglu/godot-mcp
  Licensed under the MIT License.

which itself extends:

  godot-mcp by Solomon Elias (Coding-Solo)
  https://github.com/Coding-Solo/godot-mcp
  Licensed under the MIT License.

The TypeScript sources were adapted only to embed them into this server: the
standalone MCP bootstrap (stdio transport, ListTools/CallTool request handlers,
process entry point) was removed, and the tool list is exposed via
`getToolDefinitions()` and `callTool(name, args)` so this server can register and
dispatch them through its own transport layer. The GDScript engines are
unmodified apart from an attribution header. All original copyright and license
notices are retained.

The MIT License text applies to the vendored portions; a full copy is in the
LICENSE file at the repository root, which covers this project under the same
terms.
